{"tid":791186,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚，我地一齊追憶年少時最真摯嘅初心","createTime":"2018-08-23T14:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T03:04:19.000Z","uid":191633,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46bce41c0629ea67cf6f8f78385431d7b5e58c39","tid":791186,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"你仲記唔記得細細個時第一次寫嘅「我的志願」、「我的夢想」係咩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隨住年紀增長，學識多咗，經歷多咗<br />\n我地嘅目標同人生理想不停改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有時，我地會認為自己根本無變<br />\n但其實歲月同環境已經令我地嘅初心變質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔願意承認，甚至連自己都唔知<br />\n而有好多人，已經諗爆頭都回憶唔返<br />\n對世界有認知以來，自己嘅初衷係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為呢個世界實在未如我地童年時嘅想象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地已經再無可能用盡全身力氣去完成我地嘅理想、夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每當我地一諗到「理想」、「初衷」<br />\n就自然會問「錢呢？」、「父幹呢？」<br />\n又或者「人地點諗我呢？」、「會唔會老咗個陣後悔呢？」<br />\n顧慮太多，意志太少<br />\n制肘太多，能力太少<br />\n<br />\n最後，我地唯有順從一條大路<br />\n一個推一個咁朝住同一個方向走<br />\n然後將我地曾經想象過嘅美好<br />\n放喺一個永遠唔會再踏足嘅房間<br />\n永遠咁上鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d41a3df5e6b7cefbcea1c2e4c07e4f604bb28b4","tid":791186,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"如果你有一個夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你仲年輕，仲係一張白紙<br />\n記得唔好嫌棄自己乜都無<br />\n記得唔好時刻都提自己人地有乜我都要有<br />\n人地有嘅，你未必想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實，一張白紙先係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為無任何野渲染過<br />\n你可以自由發揮你嘅想象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係一個將會永遠對自己失望嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再有人同我一樣<br />\n跌落呢個萬劫不復嘅深淵入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果你堅持，甚至已經做好跌落去嘅準備<br />\n你唯有忘記自己嘅初心<br />\n而我唯有祝福你<br />\n唔好變成下一個我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係時候，由內到外咁<br />\n執拾一下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ba5eefcf57073795b557321aa819e5d26dfc3","tid":791186,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"D飯太多，餐蛋太少"},{"pid":"82f54772eab96601c61a49a4d5c67f26d003faf1","tid":791186,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d973ebbd98ef6732bd329041db25aafbe00fa710","tid":791186,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘 無人覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樓主細個個志願係啲咩？"},{"pid":"d4bbca1a507d4fe862878f37f6d7ec2fa7c0c882","tid":791186,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d973ebbd98ef6732bd329041db25aafbe00fa710","tid":791186,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘 無人覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樓主細個個志願係啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"無人覆唔慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘係好多野已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2598d748b2fce757b7945b801c044006c6ba63","tid":791186,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmo